PageTitle: display fwm m-lag synchronization packet statistics
FuncDef: The display fwm m-lag synchronization packet statistics command displays statistics about synchronization packets between the devices paired into a DFS group. The display fwm m-lag synchronization packet statistics command displays statistics about synchronization packets between the devices paired into a DFS group.
CLIs: display fwm m-lag synchronization packet statistics [ slot <slotid> ]

ParaDef.Info:
Specifies the slot ID.
The value is a string of 1 to 49 case-sensitive characters, spaces not supported.

Examples: <HUAWEI> display fwm m-lag synchronization packet statistics
<HUAWEI> display fwm m-lag synchronization packet statistics
